summary: 12.2.1. A. B. Biswas and Zhi-Kin Zhang are the authors of the book. The book was published by the Harvard School of Dental Medicine. It is available in hardback and paperback editions. For more information, visit: http://www.harvard.edu/dental-medicine/books/b-biswas-zhang.
